1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:03,319
[Music] Little Fox.

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:11,800
Peter and Benjamin Have a Feast, Episode One: Gathering...

3
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:23,640
[Music]

4
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:29,880
...Nuts. Peter and Benjamin were planning a harvest feast.

5
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:35,879
"We need berries," Peter said.

6
00:00:35,879 --> 00:00:44,079
"Let's gather some nuts too," Benjamin said.

7
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:53,040
"A harvest feast must have nuts."

8
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:56,140
The bunnies gathered some berries.

9
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:12,820
Then they looked for nuts.

10
00:01:12,820 --> 00:01:16,280
Peter and Benjamin saw lots of squirrels.

11
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:22,140
The squirrels were gathering nuts for winter.

12
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:29,920
It was hard work.

13
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:33,479
Peter and Benjamin put their nuts in a pile.

14
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:35,320
"We have a big pile now," Peter said.

15
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:42,640
"Hey!" shouted a squirrel. It was Timmy Tiptoes.

16
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:46,360
Timmy ran toward the bunnies. He pointed at their big pile.

17
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:50,759
"Are you stealing my nuts?" he asked.

18
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:57,119
Timmy looked at Benjamin and Peter.

19
00:01:57,119 --> 00:02:00,119
"No," Peter said. "We collected these nuts."

20
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:08,440
"Hmph," Timmy looked mad. "I put my nuts right there."

21
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:13,519
"Well, these are our nuts," Benjamin said.

22
00:02:13,519 --> 00:02:20,940
Timmy frowned. "Then where are my nuts?"

23
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:26,319
Benjamin shrugged. "I don't know."

24
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:36,839
"But we will find out," Peter said.

25
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:46,080
Peter and Benjamin Have a Feast, Episode Two: The Nut Thief.

26
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:14,620
Peter and Benjamin looked for the missing nuts.

27
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:27,959
Timmy gathered new ones.

28
00:03:27,959 --> 00:03:34,480
"The squirrels are very busy," Peter said. "They are gathering lots of nuts."

29
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:42,920
"Winter is coming," Benjamin said. "They need—"

30
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:45,920
"Hey!" a squirrel suddenly shouted. "Look at my pile!"

31
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:52,959
A second squirrel cried, "Who stole my nuts?" A third squirrel yelled.

32
00:03:52,959 --> 00:03:58,680
More squirrels came running.

33
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:04,200
One squirrel shouted at Timmy Tiptoes. "Did you steal our nuts?" she cried.

34
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:12,360
"No," Timmy said. "Someone took some of my nuts too."

35
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:19,560
"There is a nut thief!" the squirrels shouted back and forth.

36
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:29,440
Just then, Peter spotted a fat squirrel. "Look, Benjamin," Peter whispered. "It's Silvertail."

37
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:38,240
Silvertail slipped over to the nut piles.

38
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:47,080
The squirrels were still fighting. They did not see Silvertail. He took nuts from a pile.

39
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:12,960
Silvertail hid the nuts under a log.

40
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:19,680
Then he laughed. "I have lots of nuts for winter. I don't have to work at all!"

41
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:44,529
Peter and Benjamin Have a Feast, Episode Three: Silvertail.

42
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:55,520
Peter looked at Benjamin. "Silvertail is the nut thief."

43
00:05:55,520 --> 00:06:03,759
The bunnies ran to the squirrels. "We found the nut thief," Peter said.

44
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:11,520
"Go away," a squirrel said. "This is not bunny business."

45
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:16,840
Another yelled, "It is squirrel business."

46
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:23,680
Timmy looked at the bunnies. "Who is the nut thief?" he asked.

47
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:30,350
"Come with us," Benjamin said. "We will show you." Timmy followed the bunnies.

48
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:48,720
They showed him Silvertail's hiding spot. Timmy's eyes got big.

49
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:55,240
"Wow," he said. "Silvertail is stealing our nuts. We must stop him."

50
00:06:55,240 --> 00:07:05,360
Benjamin saw a hollow tree. It had a hole in its trunk. "Hmm," Benjamin said. "I have an idea."

51
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:15,240
The bunnies got some nuts.

52
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:23,670
They hopped to the hollow tree. Then they pushed the nuts into the hole.

53
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:31,520
"Now let's find Silvertail," Benjamin said.

54
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:55,479
Silvertail was taking a nap. "Hi, Silvertail!" Peter woke him up.

55
00:07:55,479 --> 00:08:03,319
"We found lots of nuts. Would you like some?"

56
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:14,000
"Yes," Silvertail licked his lips. "Where are they?"

57
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:22,400
Peter and Benjamin Have a Feast, Episode 4: The Harvest Feast.

58
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:29,599
The bunnies brought Silvertail to the tree.

59
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:38,760
Silvertail looked in the hole. "I don't see any nuts."

60
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:47,760
Silvertail bent deeper. "Where are—" "Yikes!" Silvertail fell into the hole.

61
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:56,920
"Help!" he cried. "Oh, I'm stuck!" The bunnies laughed.

62
00:08:57,720 --> 00:09:06,890
"The nut thief is trapped," Peter said. "Goodbye, Silvertail," Benjamin said.

63
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:19,279
The bunnies told the squirrels about Silvertail. The squirrels stopped fighting.

64
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:26,640
"I have a great idea," Timmy said. "Let's share our nuts."

65
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:38,160
The squirrels shared all the nuts. Timmy gave some to the bunnies.

66
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:45,990
"Thank you for helping us," Timmy said. "We can save these nuts for our feast," Peter said.

67
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:59,320
At last, it was time for the harvest feast. All the squirrels came.

68
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:12,040
Timmy rubbed his belly. "These nut pies are delicious!"

69
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:18,279
Then someone else appeared. Peter gasped. "Silvertail!"

70
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:29,000
Benjamin laughed. "He's not fat anymore." Silvertail frowned at the bunnies.

71
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:35,519
"You trapped me in the tree! And where... where are all my nuts?"

72
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:42,440
Peter pointed to the nut pies. "Right there." Everyone but Silvertail laughed.